00:00:41.140 --> 00:00:52.140
Satan's system has developed the art of shaping the minds of people into fragile glass vessels with little useful purpose.

00:00:53.140 --> 00:01:05.450
In fact, Romans 9.22 refers to such ones as vessels of wrath made fit for destruction. Find with me, Romans 12.2.

00:01:05.450 --> 00:01:13.450
What is responsible for molding and shaping the inclinations of the people of the world?

00:01:14.450 --> 00:01:29.450
